-- Lanxess Raises 2010 Earnings Forecast as Rubber Demand Gains, Net Surges
-- Benedikt Kammel
-- 2010-08-06T05:33:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/lanxess-raises-2010-earnings-forecast-as-rubber-demand-gains-net-surges.html

          
          
             Lanxess AG said it raised its outlook
for the full year to earnings before interest, tax, depreciation
and amortization before special items of about 800 million
euros, from a previous prediction of as much as 700 million
euros.  
          
          


  


        